<item>
 <title>WRI: 863 Program&#039;s Energy Focus - 11th Five Year Plan</title>
 <link>http://www.chinafaqs.org/library/wri-863-programs-energy-focus-11th-five-year-plan</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-filefield field-field-image&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;img src=&quot;http://www.chinafaqs.org/files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/an_emerging_revolution-4.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;106&quot; class=&quot;imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default&quot;/&gt;        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-filefield field-field-library-file&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Library File:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;div class=&quot;filefield-file&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;filefield-icon field-icon-application-pdf&quot;  alt=&quot;application/pdf icon&quot; src=&quot;http://www.chinafaqs.org/sites/all/modules/filefield/icons/application-pdf.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chinafaqs.org/files/chinainfo/wri_863_programs_energy_focus.pdf&quot; type=&quot;application/pdf; length=274924&quot;&gt;wri_863_programs_energy_focus.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-text field-field-author&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Author:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
                    World Resources Institute        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Also known as the State High-Tech Development Plan, the 863 Program was created to stimulate the development of advanced technologies in a wide range of fields in order to render China independent of financial obligations for foreign technologies. The program has changing focuses and priorities, depending on the needs of national economic development. During the 11th Five Year Plan, the 863 program set up 10 focus areas, including energy technologies. Within the energy category there are four technology priorities: hydrogen and fuel cell, energy efficiency, clean coal and renewable energy. A total of 1.12 billion yuan ($172 million) has been invested in these priorities, with hydrogen and efficiency technologies receiving the majority of funding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chinafaqs.org/library/wri-863-programs-energy-focus-11th-five-year-plan&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;read more&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
 <category domain="http://www.chinafaqs.org/category/type/graphics">Graphics</category>
 <category domain="http://www.chinafaqs.org/category/issue-areas/renewables-and-alternative-energy">Renewables and Alternative Energy</category>
 <pubDate>Mon, 01 Mar 2010 22:09:16 +0000</pubDate>
 <dc:creator>nprice</dc:creator>
 <guid isPermaLink="false">313 at http://www.chinafaqs.org</guid>
</item>
<item>
 <title>WRI: Government Funded R&amp;D in China</title>
 <link>http://www.chinafaqs.org/library/wri-government-funded-rd-china</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-filefield field-field-image&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;img src=&quot;http://www.chinafaqs.org/files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/an_emerging_revolution-3_0.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;196&quot; height=&quot;120&quot; class=&quot;imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default&quot;/&gt;        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-filefield field-field-library-file&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Library File:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
                    &lt;div class=&quot;filefield-file&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;filefield-icon field-icon-application-pdf&quot;  alt=&quot;application/pdf icon&quot; src=&quot;http://www.chinafaqs.org/sites/all/modules/filefield/icons/application-pdf.png&quot; /&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chinafaqs.org/files/chinainfo/wri_government_funded_r%2526d_in_china.pdf&quot; type=&quot;application/pdf; length=1171487&quot;&gt;wri_government_funded_r&amp;amp;d_in_china.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-text field-field-author&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Author:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;
                    World Resources Institute        &lt;/div&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the past five years government R&amp;amp;D appropriations have increased dramatically, from 70.3 billion yuan ($11 bil) in 2001 to 168.9 billion yuan ($26 bil) in 2006. As a result, the share of R&amp;amp;D in total government expenditure increased from 3.7% to 4.2% from 2001 - 2006 (MOST 2007). Among the various publicly-funded S&amp;amp;T programs, the 863 &amp;amp; 973 programs provide the most direct funding sources for clean technologies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.chinafaqs.org/library/wri-government-funded-rd-china&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;read more&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
